            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="20.0" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform Process Steward: Moore, Kimberly &lt;kimberly.moore@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champion: Bowers, Colleen &lt;colleen.bowers@intel.com&gt;  of any changes that occur within the flow from now onwards so that changes can be accurately reflected within BIC</text>
